{"published time": "2024-03-05T23-59-00-00-00", "images": ["https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_ananindeua_pa-1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_barra_mansa_rj_3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_rio_de_janeiro_rj_2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_7.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_2_parque_de_exposicoes_regiao_vale_do_jamari.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil2-1024x768.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil3-1024x768.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil4-1024x771.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_1-1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_2-1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_1.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_2.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"682\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <p>\n  <em>\n   Featured image: Banner with the slogans \u201cLong live the Heroic Palestinian Resistance Struggle!\u201d and \u201cIt is right to rebel\u201d at demonstration in support of the Palestinian people, Aalborg, Denmark, 2\n   <sup>\n    nd\n   </sup>\n   of march. Source: Socialist Revolution\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p>\n  The State of Israel continues to develop its genocide against the Palestinian people, with the\n  <a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/longform/2023/10/9/israel-hamas-war-in-maps-and-charts-live-tracker\">\n   latest death toll\n  </a>\n  in Gaza of at least 31.052 people, in addition to more than 72.043 injured and more that 8.000 missing. In the West Bank at least 421 people have been killed, and more than 4.600 have been injured. According to the UN, 360,000 residential units, more than half of the homes in Gaza, have been damaged or destroyed. 132 water wells are damaged or destroyed and only 11 out of 35 hospitals are partially functioning.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Every hour 15 people are killed, including 6 children, 35 people are injured, and 12 buildings are destroyed.\n </p>\n <p>\n  The State of Israel and imperialism continue with their\n  <a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/3/4/reasonable-grounds-to-believe-hamas-committed-sexual-violence-un\">\n   claims of sexual violence\n  </a>\n  being committed by fighters of the National Resistance, with a UN report claiming there are \u201creasonable grounds\u201d to believe the claims are true. However, the UN team who made the report said they were not able to meet any victims of sexual violence. Israel\n  <a href=\"https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/un-report-clear-evidence-of-sexual-violence-rape-during-and-after-hamas-oct-7-attack/0000018e-0b47-d3bd-afce-bbc7a2ac0000\">\n   rejects\n  </a>\n  investigations of the many accusations of sexual violence committed by themselves.\n </p>\n <p>\n  The State of Israel continues\n  <a href=\"https://aje.io/lxyadi?update=2750690\">\n   exchanging fire\n  </a>\n  with Hezbollah along the Israel-Lebanon border. Hezbollah has reported to have achieved a\n  <a href=\"https://aje.io/lxyadi?update=2750473\">\n   direct hit\n  </a>\n  against a mechanized Israeli military force at the Birkat Risha outpost in northern Israel with a missile strike today at 12:05.\n </p>\n <p>\n  New actions of solidarity with the Palestinian people and the National Resistance Front of Palestine.\n </p>\n <p>\n  In the Red Sea, a\n  <a href=\"https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/3/2/rubymar-cargo-ship-earlier-hit-by-houthis-has-sunk-yemeni-government-says\">\n   British cargo ship sank\n  </a>\n  after being hit by Ansar Allah (the \u2018Houthies\u2019). Ansar Allah, who governs the capital of Yemen as well as most of its populated territory, have targeted ships linked to Israel as well as Yankee and British imperialism, in support of the Palestinian people who are facing genocide. The campaign has forced many ships to take the much longer route around Africa.\n </p>\n <p>\n  In Brazil the Revolutionary Front for the Defense of the Rights of the People (FRDDP \u2013 Brasil) continues developing its\n  <a href=\"https://serviraopovo.com.br/2024/02/20/palestina-resiste-frente-revolucionaria-de-defesa-dos-direitos-do-povo-frddp-brasil/\">\n   powerful campaign\n  </a>\n  under the slogan \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine will Triumph\u201d.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9532\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"512\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_ananindeua_pa-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_ananindeua_pa-1.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine Will Triumph\u201d, FRDDP - Brazil, Ananindeua, Par\u00e1, Brazil. Source: serve the people\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9533\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_barra_mansa_rj_3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_barra_mansa_rj_3.webp\" width=\"575\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine Will Triumph\u201d, FRDDP - Brazil, Barra Mansa, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Source: serve the people\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9536\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"482\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_rio_de_janeiro_rj_2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_rio_de_janeiro_rj_2.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine Will Triumph\u201d, FRDDP - Brazil, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Source: serve the people\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9534\" data-id=\"9534\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"513\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_3.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9535\" data-id=\"9535\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"513\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_7.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_francisco_beltrao_pr_7.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine Will Triumph\u201d, FRDDP - Brazil, Francisco Beltr\u00e3o, Paran\u00e1, Brazil. Source: serve the people\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9537\" data-id=\"9537\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"521\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_1.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9538\" data-id=\"9538\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"454\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_2_parque_de_exposicoes_regiao_vale_do_jamari.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/palestina_theobroma_ro_2_parque_de_exposicoes_regiao_vale_do_jamari.webp\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   \u201cPalestine Resists, Palestine Will Triumph\u201d, FRDDP - Brazil, Theobroma, Rond\u00f4nia, Brazil. Source: serve the people\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <iframe allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/897346364?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" title=\"palestina_nordeste\" width=\"1024\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <iframe allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"576\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/897346303?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963\" title=\"palestina_belem_pa\" width=\"1024\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  On the 29\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of February in the Federal State of\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/mg-protesto-na-frente-da-globo-denuncia-cumplicidade-dos-monopolios-de-imprensa-com-o-genocidio-palestino/\">\n   Minas Gerais\n  </a>\n  , Brazil, hundreds of people protested in front of the headquarters of the Brazilian press monopoly Rede Globo, denouncing its pro-Zionist coverage. The protest was called for by the Minas Gerais Committee for Solidarity with the Palestinian People. The protest also expressed their outrage over the more than 100 Palestinians who were executed while waiting for aid.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9523\" data-id=\"9523\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"771\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil1.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9525\" data-id=\"9525\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil2-1024x768.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil2-1024x768.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9526\" data-id=\"9526\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"768\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil3-1024x768.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil3-1024x768.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9527\" data-id=\"9527\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"771\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil4-1024x771.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Brazil4-1024x771.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Protest in front of the headquarters of Rede Globo, Minas Gerais, 29\n   <sup>\n    th\n   </sup>\n   of February. Source: AND\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  On the 2\n  <sup>\n   nd\n  </sup>\n  of March in the city of\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ce-ativistas-agitam-capital-cearense-com-panfletagem-pro-palestina/\">\n   Fortaleza,\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ce-ativistas-agitam-capital-cearense-com-panfletagem-pro-palestina/\">\n   Cear\u00e1\n  </a>\n  , Brazil, the Cear\u00e1 Front to Support the Palestinian Resistance carried out agitation \u201cin memory of the more than 112 murdered in the flour massacre, for the end of Zionism and the murderous State of Israel and in defense of the Palestinian people and of the Palestinian National Resistance\u201d. Part of the masses spontaneously showed support with slogans such as \u201cLong live free Palestine\u201d. Also here the press monopolies, who portrayed the massacre as \u201cconfusion\u201d, were denounced.\n </p>\n <p>\n  On the 2\n  <sup>\n   nd\n  </sup>\n  of March in\n  <a href=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/04/aalborg-kraftfuld-demonstration-for-palaestina/\">\n   Denmark\n  </a>\n  , many demonstrations took place across the country, under the main slogan \u201cAll of Denmark on the streets for Palestine\u201d. In the demonstration in Aalborg, The Anti-Imperialist Collective made a speech condemning Israel\u2019s genocide in Gaza, expressed its full and unconditional support to the Palestinian people who are fighting for liberation with arms in hand, and condemned the attack on Yemen by Yankee and Danish imperialism.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9528\" data-id=\"9528\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_1-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_1-1.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9529\" data-id=\"9529\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_2-1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Denmark_2-1.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-caption wp-element-caption\">\n   Demonstration in support of the Palestinian people, Aalborg, Denmark, 2\n   <sup>\n    nd\n   </sup>\n   of march. Source: Socialist Revolution\n  </figcaption>\n </figure>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9522\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"682\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Featured_Palestine-Denmark_3.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Banner with the slogans \u201cLong live the Heroic Palestinian Resistance Struggle!\u201d and \u201cIt is right to rebel\u201d. Source: Socialistisk Revolution\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  In Toulouse, France, Palestine Support Committee 31, which the LJR participated in, have carried out an action for the boycott of Carrefour, a French retail monopoly which has had branches in Israel since 2022.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-dnt=\"true\" data-width=\"550\">\n    <p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"fr\">\n     \ud83d\udccdToulouse\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     \u25b6 \ufe0fThe LJR actively participates in the Palestine 31 support committee which leads the boycott against Carrefour!\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     \ud83d\udd25Cit the genocide in Palestine, denounce the imperialists who finance it!\n     <br/>\n     <br/>\n     Palestine will win ! Support resistance, organize yourself! \ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\uddf8\n     <a href=\"https://t.co/QEyo9brNqW\">\n      pic.twitter.com/QEyo9brNqW\n     </a>\n    </p>\n    - Revolutionary Youth League (@Liguej_R)\n    <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LigueJ_R/status/1764972037737414877?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">\n     March 5, 2024\n    </a>\n   </blockquote>\n   <script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\">\n   </script>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  On the 3\n  <sup>\n   rd\n  </sup>\n  of March pro-Palestine and revolutionary demonstrators protested against the inauguration of Finland\u2019s new president Alexander Stubb. An\n  <a href=\"/home/amnesia/Persistent/Meetings/2024-03-05/publish/Palestine/protested%20against%20the%20inauguration\">\n   article\n  </a>\n  in Punalippu denounced how bourgeois media ignored the protest to create a fictitious image of popular consensus. In videos by the bourgeois media continuous shouting of \u201cSlaughterer!\u201d is clearly heard in the background, while the media either ignored it, or made claims such as that people were shouting to congratulate the new president. It is even shown in the videos that the new president is discussing the protests with the out-going president, and even pointing at the protest.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9530\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"516\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_1.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_1.webp\" width=\"598\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Finish politician Otto Meri was outraged by the \u201cMaoist Palestinian tricksters\u201d. Source: X\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9531\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"360\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palestine-Finland_2.webp\" width=\"640\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Finnish President Stubb points out the protesters to outgoing president Niinist\u00f6. Screenshot from HS-IS video\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://redherald.org/2024/03/05/update-on-palestine-2/", "type": "article", "title": "Update on Palestine \u2013 The Red Herald", "description": "The State of Israel continues to develop its genocide against the Palestinian people, with the latest death toll in Gaza of at least 31.052 people", "modified time": "2024-03-05T22:48:08+00:00", "author": ["G.D."], "categories": ["Asia", "Featured", "International"], "tags": ["Israel", "Palestine", "Struggle for land"], "sections": ["Asia", "Featured", "International", "Israel", "Palestine", "Struggle for land", "English", "pll_65e7a227be5a1"]}